    "Moreover, the emphasis on adaptability and security ensures that the framework will remain relevant and ethically grounded as technology and medical knowledge advance.",
    "In conclusion, this study marks the initiation of an ambitious journey towards redefining precision medicine through AI.",
    "The future projects inspired by this research aim to build upon the established foundation, striving for a data pipeline that is not only more comprehensive and detailed but also adaptable to the evolving landscape of healthcare and technology.",
